28:20.657 --> 28:22.700
- Let's go, Eagles!

28:22.784 --> 28:26.621
♪ ♪

28:26.704 --> 28:29.624
<i>[dark music]</i>

28:29.707 --> 28:31.543
<i>♪ ♪</i>

28:31.626 --> 28:34.546
[cheers and applause]

28:34.629 --> 28:36.714
<i>♪ ♪</i>

28:36.798 --> 28:41.302
<i>- Direct your attention</i>
<i>to midfield for the coin toss.</i>

28:41.386 --> 28:43.346
- This is such bullshit.

28:43.430 --> 28:45.056
The crowd's here
to see us not them

28:45.140 --> 28:47.851
<i>[marching band playing]</i>

28:47.934 --> 28:51.813
[cheers and applause]

28:51.896 --> 28:53.273
- I need to talk to you.

28:53.356 --> 28:56.609
- Now is not a good time.

28:58.069 --> 29:00.947
<i>- Coin toss goes</i>
<i>to Sutton Grove.</i>

29:01.030 --> 29:04.033
[cheering]

29:07.036 --> 29:09.622
<i>But before we begin tonight,</i>

29:09.706 --> 29:11.207
<i>many of</i>
<i>the students here knew</i>

29:11.291 --> 29:13.334
<i>Sergeant William H. Mosley</i>

29:13.418 --> 29:15.628
<i>as a mentor, a friend.</i>

29:15.712 --> 29:18.006
<i>And we want</i>
<i>to mark his passing tonight.</i>

29:18.089 --> 29:22.177
<i>One of his trusted men,</i>
<i>PFC James Tibbs,</i>

29:22.260 --> 29:25.013
<i>will lead us</i>
<i>in a moment of silence.</i>

29:31.603 --> 29:34.230
- Sergeant Mosley...

29:35.815 --> 29:38.026
You will not be forgotten.

29:46.910 --> 29:50.330
You will not be forgotten!

29:50.413 --> 29:53.333
<i>[somber tone]</i>

29:53.416 --> 30:00.423
<i>♪ ♪</i>

30:15.939 --> 30:18.525
<i>- Thank you, and good luck</i>
<i>tonight, Sutton Grove.</i>

30:18.608 --> 30:21.611
[cheers and applause]

30:29.702 --> 30:32.455
- Kurtz is saying things
about you.

30:32.539 --> 30:34.499
Stuff that doesn't make sense
to me.

30:34.582 --> 30:36.251
- You're gonna listen to Kurtz?

30:37.418 --> 30:39.254
I told you,
I have this under control.

30:39.337 --> 30:40.463
[cheering]

30:40.547 --> 30:44.092
Okay?
- You keep saying that.

30:44.175 --> 30:46.886
But Coach,
you called me that night.

30:46.970 --> 30:49.222
And you brought me into
this horrible thing,

30:49.305 --> 30:51.432
and you owe me the truth.
- You know the truth.

30:51.516 --> 30:53.142
I know what's happening here.
This is Beth.

30:53.226 --> 30:54.894
She has you brainwashed,
and she always has.

30:54.978 --> 30:58.106
You need to grow up
and cut her loose.

31:00.275 --> 31:01.943
It's time, Addy.

31:02.026 --> 31:05.029
[cheering]

31:11.077 --> 31:12.078
all: Okay!

31:12.161 --> 31:14.914
Attack, attack
that quarterback.

31:14.998 --> 31:17.584
Knock him flat,
right on his back.

31:17.667 --> 31:20.336
Attack, attack
that quarterback.

31:20.420 --> 31:22.922
Knock him flat,
right on his back.

31:23.006 --> 31:24.132
- [whistle blows]
- Ready?

31:24.215 --> 31:25.675
all: Okay!

31:25.758 --> 31:27.927
Attack, attack
that quarterback.

31:28.011 --> 31:29.304
- Ready!
all: Knock him flat,

31:29.387 --> 31:31.264
right on his back.

31:31.347 --> 31:33.933
[cheering, whistle blows]

31:34.017 --> 31:37.061
<i>[upbeat dance music]</i>

31:37.145 --> 31:39.898
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:39.981 --> 31:41.941
- Down!

31:42.025 --> 31:43.943
25's a Mike!
25's a Mike!

31:44.027 --> 31:46.029
- Read, set, hike!

31:46.112 --> 31:49.115
<i>♪ ♪</i>

31:49.198 --> 31:50.116
[whistle blows]
<i>- Touchdown!</i>

31:50.199 --> 31:52.243
- Oh, yes!
- Yes!

31:52.327 --> 31:53.536
[laughs]

31:53.620 --> 31:56.956
[cheering]

31:57.040 --> 31:58.291
- Let's go!

31:58.374 --> 31:59.584
- I don't wanna jinx it,
but I think there's a chance

31:59.667 --> 32:01.085
we could actually
win this game.

32:01.169 --> 32:02.462
[both laugh]

32:02.545 --> 32:04.297
I forgot,
did you play in high school?

32:04.380 --> 32:06.633
- Oh, no, no.
Tennis team.

32:06.716 --> 32:08.092
- Ah, well,
there's a little insight

32:08.176 --> 32:09.802
into Matt French's past, right?

32:09.886 --> 32:11.179
all: Non-stop!

32:11.262 --> 32:12.680
We're taking it to the top.

32:12.764 --> 32:14.390
- Prep school, locked jaw,
gin and tonics.

32:14.474 --> 32:15.558
Am I right?

32:15.642 --> 32:18.061
Class act.
Ah, speaking of class acts,

32:18.144 --> 32:20.021
there's our rainmaker,
our power broker.

32:20.104 --> 32:22.398
Play nice.
- Ah, just a mom today.

32:22.482 --> 32:24.525
- All right.
- [laughs]

32:24.609 --> 32:27.278
all: Non-stop!
We're takin' it to the top!

32:27.362 --> 32:28.446
- You'll see.

32:28.529 --> 32:29.614
That'll be your
baby girl down there

32:29.697 --> 32:31.240
before you know it.
- Mm-hmm.

32:31.324 --> 32:32.951
Never knew
I had so many feelings

32:33.034 --> 32:34.202
until I had them.

32:34.285 --> 32:36.454
all: We're takin' it
to the top!

32:36.537 --> 32:37.705
Non-stop!

32:37.789 --> 32:40.333
- One minute,
it's all about you.

32:40.416 --> 32:43.086
Your career, your dreams,

32:43.169 --> 32:45.713
your ambitions.

32:45.797 --> 32:49.175
And then suddenly,
they're there.

32:49.258 --> 32:52.136
And you'd do anything for them,

32:52.220 --> 32:54.847
to protect them.

32:54.931 --> 32:58.184
- The things we do for them.

32:58.267 --> 33:00.645
To make up for
the things we do to them.

33:00.728 --> 33:01.646
[whistle blows]

33:01.729 --> 33:04.607
[cheering]

33:04.691 --> 33:08.152
- Okay, squad.
Who's ready?

33:08.236 --> 33:09.570
Dead Man's Fall.

33:09.654 --> 33:11.489
The quick and dirty one.

33:11.572 --> 33:12.907
Guns out, bitches.

33:12.991 --> 33:15.576
- We're taking the field?
- Next jump-out.

33:15.660 --> 33:17.954
- But Coach--
- Yeah, shouldn't we ask her?

33:18.037 --> 33:19.455
- You wanna ask Coach
if she can help us

33:19.539 --> 33:21.040
with our Dead Man?

33:23.042 --> 33:25.503
<i>- Timeout, Bobcats.</i>

33:25.586 --> 33:26.921
- That's our cue.

33:27.005 --> 33:30.550
<i>[tense music]</i>

33:30.633 --> 33:33.469
You ready, Addy?

33:33.553 --> 33:36.806
Sure hope you catch me
when I fall.

33:40.226 --> 33:45.064
<i>♪ ♪</i>

33:45.148 --> 33:47.483
all: Guns up till sunup!

33:47.567 --> 33:50.570
Gotta get our guns up!

33:50.653 --> 33:52.822
Guns up till sunup!

33:52.905 --> 33:55.616
Ain't nobody
gonna fuck with us!

33:55.700 --> 33:57.952
Guns up till sunup!

33:58.036 --> 34:01.414
Gonna get our guns up!

34:01.497 --> 34:03.207
[imitating gunfire]

34:05.626 --> 34:08.004
Ain't nobody gonna stop us!

34:08.087 --> 34:10.923
Guns up till sunup!

34:11.007 --> 34:13.217
Gotta get our guns up!

34:13.301 --> 34:20.308
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:21.184 --> 34:23.352
Ain't nobody gonna stop us!

34:23.436 --> 34:25.938
- Eyes on your girl.
- [pants]

34:28.941 --> 34:30.568
<i>- Sutton Grove,</i>
<i>coming back strong</i>

34:30.651 --> 34:31.903
<i>after that time out.</i>

34:31.986 --> 34:35.156
<i>[dark tone]</i>

34:35.239 --> 34:40.828
<i>♪ ♪</i>

34:40.912 --> 34:43.206
Hey, hey, hey, hey,
What's the holdup?

34:43.289 --> 34:44.415
Kurtz?

34:44.499 --> 34:51.506
<i>♪ ♪</i>

35:03.101 --> 35:04.727
<i>- And that's the game, folks.</i>

35:04.811 --> 35:06.395
<i>Eagles for the win.</i>

35:06.479 --> 35:08.981
[cheering]

35:09.065 --> 35:13.820
<i>[marching band plays]</i>

35:13.903 --> 35:15.696
- Addy.

35:15.780 --> 35:17.615
Addy.
- Stop.

35:19.075 --> 35:20.868
- Addy--
- I said stop, Beth.

35:20.952 --> 35:24.163
- Addy, where is your Hamsa?

35:24.247 --> 35:26.999
- What is it with you
and this fucking bracelet?

35:27.083 --> 35:29.043
- Wait, you mean the bracelet
that I gave to you

35:29.127 --> 35:30.628
and that you gave to her?

35:30.711 --> 35:32.672
- I didn't.

35:32.755 --> 35:35.550
- Your lies, Addy, you can't
even keep track of them.

35:35.633 --> 35:40.721
Addy, wake the fuck up,
please.

35:40.805 --> 35:43.266
You were there.

35:43.349 --> 35:45.101
Somehow, Addy,

35:45.184 --> 35:47.395
somehow you were there.

35:47.478 --> 35:48.521
- No, I wasn't.

35:48.604 --> 35:50.773
You don't know everything.

35:50.857 --> 35:53.776
Okay?
And you don't control me.

35:53.860 --> 35:55.278
- No, I know
just who controls you.

35:55.361 --> 35:57.780
- I control me.

35:57.864 --> 35:59.866
And you need to stop this.

35:59.949 --> 36:01.951
You have to stop this
for me.

36:02.034 --> 36:05.580
- This is for you, okay?

36:05.663 --> 36:08.833
You think that she's gonna
protect you, she won't.

36:08.916 --> 36:12.670
She does whatever she wants
and she takes and she takes,

36:12.753 --> 36:14.922
and she--
- That's you, Beth!

36:15.006 --> 36:16.799
That's you.

36:16.883 --> 36:18.926
You take.

36:19.010 --> 36:21.345
- Is that what you think?

36:21.429 --> 36:24.390
Is that
what you actually think?

36:24.473 --> 36:26.517
- Yeah.

36:29.145 --> 36:31.647
- Well, I guess we'll see,
won't we?

36:31.731 --> 36:33.524
We'll see if she's worth it.

36:33.608 --> 36:36.235
If she's got your back
like I always had.

36:36.319 --> 36:39.947
Eyes on my girl, Addy.

36:40.031 --> 36:41.824
We'll see what she says
when the detectives

36:41.908 --> 36:44.285
ask about the bracelet.

36:44.368 --> 36:46.412
Your bracelet.

36:46.495 --> 36:48.748
The one that they found
at the crime scene.

36:49.916 --> 36:51.542
- What?

36:53.461 --> 36:56.297
What did you just say?

36:57.673 --> 37:00.384
That's not true.

37:00.468 --> 37:02.845
That's not true.
- Addy.

37:02.929 --> 37:05.139
- And even if it was,

37:05.223 --> 37:07.642
how would you know that?

37:08.976 --> 37:11.520
How could you possibly
fucking know that, Beth?

37:11.604 --> 37:13.356
- We won!
- This is insane!

37:13.439 --> 37:14.523
- Yeah, it is.

37:14.607 --> 37:15.775
- There's gonna be
a rager at Lanvers,

37:15.858 --> 37:17.944
partying over the abyss.

37:18.027 --> 37:20.363
[laughing]

37:20.446 --> 37:23.532
- The abyss.

37:23.616 --> 37:25.701
The abyss.

37:25.785 --> 37:27.370
<i>C'est moi.</i>

37:29.789 --> 37:32.375
Let's go, my band of bitches.

37:32.458 --> 37:34.252
Whoo!

37:41.008 --> 37:43.928
[Savages' "Adore"]

37:44.011 --> 37:51.018
<i>♪ ♪</i>

37:54.855 --> 37:58.067
<i>- ♪ If only</i>
<i>I didn't want the world ♪</i>

